thread.title: Local News: After massive Kitale performance, Christ Cycoz set to rock Daystar University this Thursday
thread.title_full: Local News: After massive Kitale performance, Christ Cycoz set to rock Daystar University this Thursday

title: Local News: After massive Kitale performance, Christ Cycoz set to rock Daystar University this Thursday
text:
By Njambi Mungai Tuesday, Oct 13th 2015 at 08:32 
By Njambi Mungai ( @njambie ) 
After thrilling fans at the Moi University, Kitale campus last week, the gospel trio Christ Cycoz will be pitching tent at the Daystar University this Thursday. 
In the concert dubbed Itakua Ngori, the Groove award winning trio will perform alongside Kelele Takatifu with their No No No,Some More and Sifa hits. Joining them will be the dance troupe Jims and Dims. 
Kicking off at 7pm till 10pm come dance to the urban sounds of Kelele Takatifu and Christ Cycoz. 
Entry is absolutely free.
